[[File:Liet-etno-regionai.png|thumb|right|300px|Regions within borders of modern Lithuania. Based on the map approved by Council for the Protection of Ethnic Culture, a special council established by [[Seimas]].
{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|
{{legend|#e6fefe|[[Lithuania Minor]](Mažoji Lietuva)}}
{{legend|#eafeea|[[Samogitia]](Žemaitija)}}
